Description:
    Creates a new plugin with the given name in the specified directory

Usage:
    rails generate proyeksi_app:plugin NAME DIRECTORY

Example:
    rails generate open_project:plugin stuff ~/

    This will create:
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/CHANGELOG.md
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/openproject-stuff.gemspec
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/lib
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/lib/openproject-stuff.rb
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/lib/proyeksi_app
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/lib/proyeksi_app/stuff.rb
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/lib/proyeksi_app/stuff
        ~/proyeksiapp-stuff/lib/proyeksi_app/stuff/engine.rb
